channel.title: OMG...HELP! It won't let me change anything on my server!
channel.description:
[s]Well, you might've seen my other posts...You might've also seen how many replies I got, and that nothing they said seemed to help. Well, nothing will...for those problems anyway...because, it won't let me change anything on my server? I mean, I can save the file alright yeah, but the changes won't go into affect. YES, I compiled plenty of times, YES i'm logged out of my server...so why? I'm getting 2 errors when I compile...but I doubt they have anything to do with this problem..[/S] [s] The first one says: [code]client.java:10509: illegal character: \92[/code]
[/s] [s] The second one says... [code]client.java:12695: ';' expected[/code] [/s] [s]
Thanks...PLEASE help.[/s]
MY PROBLEM IS SOLVED! PLEASE LOCK!
